{"tid":1336420,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"張國榮「復活」轉行揸巴士？","createTime":"2019-07-21T03:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T05:04:19.000Z","uid":183383,"like":3,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"50fbac53f5443b3db2b152828af2da00534d0ac8","tid":1336420,"uid":183383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T03:09:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JS-Je5u8hn4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJS-Je5u8hn4&d=3A6Iqvk0VBPdaidkhJ82Wwy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=998bffe2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JS-Je5u8hn4</a><br />\n張國榮（哥哥）逝世已16年，其風采依然長留粉絲心中。每年生忌和死忌，世界各地粉絲都會為偶像舉行悼念活動。近日網上流傳疑似張國榮在內地揸巴士的相片，見司機外形、樣貌、神情、眼神以至髮型，與張國榮猶如倒模一樣，相似程度達99%，引起網民熱烈討論。<br />\n司機：不想靠臉吃飯<br />\n<br />\n有網友表示：「真的看到哥哥了」、「這個司機真的很像哥哥，希望他真的瞞住了我們所有人，過上了平淡生活」。除了傳張國榮尚在人間外，亦有指他「復活」，有人留言：「是哥哥轉世了嗎」、「這簡直就是哥哥再生」。<br />\n<br />\n當然偶像復活只是粉絲一廂情願！有理性粉絲指「復活版張國榮」與偶像同樣帥氣，若只當巴士司機有點可惜，建議對方憑「張國榮臉」當網紅，應有更好「錢」途。結果有人留言表示真的問過對方，但他只想憑自己努力生活：「不想靠臉吃飯，這輩子只想做一個普普通通的人。」被網民讚踏實。<br />\n<br />\n傳設局扮自殺<br />\n<br />\n2003年4月1日愚人節晚上，張國榮在香港文華東方酒店二十四樓一躍而下，結束璀璨一生，但之後屢傳他仍然在世。2004年，有人言之鑿鑿指他因厭倦五光十色的生活，在親友協助下設自殺假局，並秘密坐船到南美過簡樸生活。<span style=\"color: red;\">當時有人表示在阿根廷布宜諾斯艾利斯見過張國榮的蹤影，並在網上發布一張他戴黑超的「近照」配合。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2006年，有傳導演王家衛知道張國榮尚在人間的秘密，親自到阿根廷敍舊，因而遲了抵達法國出席康城影展。直至去年亦有人在網上表示當年一名尋死的賭徒做張國榮的替身，更指張國榮現時生活得很好，只是胖了點。"},{"pid":"fda29f7dabe9d67efc7ea346b6c8a49a582726dc","tid":1336420,"uid":183383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T03:11:29.000Z","msg":"BTW今日要出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db977065f44b2afc8224f68a65a7930413a2d5e","tid":1336420,"uid":183383,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T03:11:40.000Z","msg":"3點金鐘見"},{"pid":"7fe5a4b39513f0c5f7d161edd670a520db8c230a","tid":1336420,"uid":183383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0db977065f44b2afc8224f68a65a7930413a2d5e","tid":1336420,"uid":183383,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T03:11:40.000Z","msg":"3點金鐘見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T03:11:52.000Z","msg":"維園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"febf90236c7c7c86b5f7d422ba239b12c4e1a859","tid":1336420,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T03:16:37.000Z","msg":"嗰時啲人傳乜撚嘢設局扮自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲人真係好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42da72206104f92088324758bda63161feac31b","tid":1336420,"uid":12171,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T03:19:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/e0nvNFW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe0nvNFW.gif&h=32930245&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"602e250d3237ced0ac11f716dfbde52e82997d38","tid":1336420,"uid":70439,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T03:21:46.000Z","msg":"明明係吳宗憲"},{"pid":"d0af589c58387474bed7c516f9323d15758073d5","tid":1336420,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T03:25:14.000Z","msg":"邊撚度似"},{"pid":"8f3949d057d7681769b51f72ba8817b6dc5cfa2b","tid":1336420,"uid":183383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T03:49:09.000Z","msg":"唔似咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c08fbe65666699661de3c5615452b4e2181ce9c","tid":1336420,"uid":69568,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T03:53:26.000Z","msg":"係就好呀，起碼D fans個心安樂D"},{"pid":"5793c8f34d836798a96e55eea8168f953c